<refsect1 id="description-gtksourcebuffer2">
    <title>Description</title>

<para>
The <link linkend="class-gtksourcebuffer2"><classname>gtksourceview2.Buffer</classname></link>
is the model for <link linkend="class-gtksourceview2"><classname>gtksourceview.View</classname></link>
widgets. It extends the <link linkend="class-gtktextbuffer"><classname>gtk.TextBuffer</classname></link>
object by adding features necessary to display and edit source code: syntax highlighting, bracket matching and markers. 
It also implements support for undo/redo operations.
</para>

<para>
To create a <link linkend="class-gtksourcebuffer2"><classname>gtksourceview2.Buffer</classname></link> 
use the <link linkend="constructor-gtksourcebuffer2">constructor</link>.
</para>

<para>
By default highlighting is enabled, but you can disable it with 
<link linkend="method-gtksourcebuffer2--set-highlight-syntax"><methodname>set_highlight_syntax</methodname>()</link>.
</para>
</refsect1>

